        <main id="content">
            <div id="main-overlay"></div>
            <div id="breadcrumb" class="hsection"><div class="hrow"><div class="hcol"><nav class="breadcrumb" aria-labelledby="nav_breadcrumb"><h2 id="nav_breadcrumb" class="wai-hidden">You are here</h2><ul>
<li><a href="/en/"><img src="/wp-content/themes/atosnew/images/home.svg" class="nolazy" alt="Homepage"></a></li>
<li class="breadcrumb_last" aria-current="page">Services</li>
</ul></nav></div></div></div>
            <section class="page">
                <article>
                    <header class="page__header--large "><div class="page__header-image cf" style="background-image:url(https://atos.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/team-of-three-discussing-work-banner.jpg);background-position: 70% 30%"><div class="page__header-grad"><div class="grid-row flex-grow-none"><div class="grid-col-6"><div class="header__banner-cta">
<h1>Digital solutions</h1>
<h2>from the everyday&nbsp; to the mission critical</h2>
</div></div></div></div></div></header><div class="section bg_white"><div class="grid-row"><div class="grid-col-12 gc">
<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " >
<div class="wpb_wrapper">
<h2>Designing the digital foundations for people, businesses and society to thrive</h2>
<p>Atos managed services are designed to help businesses, institutions and communities succeed and flourish. We provide the fundamental technology building blocks, the essential connections, and the expert guidance to create new digital ecosystems.</p>
<p>Our services are backed up by decades of experience and a commitment to put innovation to work creating the digital foundation for a thriving future.</p>

</div>
</div>
</div></div></div><div class="section"><div class="grid-row"><div class="grid-col-6 gc"><div class="atos_hover_block hbpart">
  <div class="atos_hover_block_image" style="height:500px;background-image: url(https://atos.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/mainframe-server-room-services-banner.jpg); background-position: center 40%;"></div>
  <div class="atos_hover_block_content shadow bg_white pad1220 hbcenter hbheight" style="margin-top: -150px"><div><h3>Cloud and Modern Infrastructure</h3>
<p>We manage, operate and modernize business-critical operations in the cloud continuum, effortlessly moving from edge to public and anything in-between.<br>
<a class="button-blue" href="/en/services/cloud-and-modern-infrastructure">Learn more</a></p>
</div></div>
</div></div><div class="grid-col-6 gc"><div class="atos_hover_block hbpart">
  <div class="atos_hover_block_image" style="height:500px;background-image: url(https://atos.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/digital-consulting-team-banner-light.jpg); background-position: 95% 30%;"></div>
  <div class="atos_hover_block_content shadow bg_white pad1220 hbcenter" style="margin-top: -150px"><div><h3>Consulting and Advisory</h3>
<p>Strategic thinking to turn complexity into clarity. We connect business insight to execution – aligning organizational goals with digital initiatives to drive measurable value, improve ROI, and accelerate long-term transformation.&nbsp;<br>
<a class="button-blue" href="https://atos.net/en/services/consulting-and-advisory">Learn more</a></p>
</div></div>
</div></div></div></div><div class="section"><div class="grid-row"><div class="grid-col-6 gc"><div class="atos_hover_block hbpart">
  <div class="atos_hover_block_image" style="height:500px;background-image: url(https://atos.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/cybersecurity-header.jpg); background-position: 60% 30%;"></div>
  <div class="atos_hover_block_content shadow bg_white pad1220 hbcenter hbheight" style="margin-top: -150px"><div><h3>Cybersecurity</h3>
<p>Protect your operations, data, and reputation with end-to-end cybersecurity backed by deep industry expertise. From strategy and testing to AI-driven managed security services, we strengthen defenses and keep you secure, compliant, and resilient in an ever-evolving threat landscape.<br>
<a class="button-blue" href="https://atos.net/en/services/cybersecurity">Learn more</a></p>
</div></div>
</div></div><div class="grid-col-6 gc"><div class="atos_hover_block hbpart">
  <div class="atos_hover_block_image" style="height:500px;background-image: url(https://atos.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/marketing-team-banner-light.jpg); background-position: 40% 25%;"></div>
  <div class="atos_hover_block_content shadow bg_white pad1220 hbcenter hbheight" style="margin-top: -150px"><div><h3>Data and AI</h3>
<p>Data platforms and AI capabilities that deliver real-time insight, automation, and growth. From governance and platform design to applied intelligence, we unlock the full value of your data.<br>
<a class="button-blue" href="https://atos.net/en/services/data-and-ai">Learn more</a></p>
</div></div>
</div></div></div></div><div class="section"><div class="grid-row"><div class="grid-col-6 gc"><div class="atos_hover_block hbpart">
  <div class="atos_hover_block_image" style="height:500px;background-image: url(https://atos.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/smiling-young-employee-banner-light.jpg); background-position: center center;"></div>
  <div class="atos_hover_block_content shadow bg_white pad1220 hbcenter hbheight" style="margin-top: -150px"><div><h3>Digital Applications</h3>
<p>Agile, scalable applications built to run your business. We modernize operations, connect experiences, and accelerate transformation – delivering the digital backbone your enterprise depends on.<br>
<a class="button-blue" href="https://atos.net/en/services/digital-applications">Learn more</a></p>
</div></div>
</div></div><div class="grid-col-6 gc"><div class="atos_hover_block hbpart">
  <div class="atos_hover_block_image" style="height:500px;background-image: url(https://atos.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/man-standing-in-office-dw-services-banner.jpg); background-position: 40% 20%;"></div>
  <div class="atos_hover_block_content shadow bg_white pad1220 hbcenter" style="margin-top: -150px"><div><h3>Digital Workplace</h3>
<p>We provide end-to-end employee experience through digital collaboration and productivity tools, as well as intelligent customer care services.<br>
<a class="button-blue" href="https://atos.net/en/services/digital-workplace">Learn more</a></p>
</div></div>
</div></div></div></div><div class="section"><div class="grid-row"><div class="grid-col-6 gc"><div class="atos_hover_block hbpart">
  <div class="atos_hover_block_image" style="height:500px;background-image: url(https://atos.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/happy-business-team-talking-on-a-meeting-at-conference-table-banner.webp); background-position: 80% 35%;"></div>
  <div class="atos_hover_block_content shadow bg_white pad1220 hbleft" style="margin-top: -150px"><div><h3>Smart Platforms</h3>
<p>Enterprise platforms optimized for speed and value. From SAP to Salesforce and ServiceNow, we accelerate platform delivery and simplify integration, powering the business-critical processes with industry-aligned solutions and proven frameworks.</p>
<div style="margin-top: 10px;"><a class="button-blue" href="https://atos.net/en/services/smart-platforms">Learn more</a></div>
</div></div>
</div></div><div class="grid-col-6 gc"><div class="atos_hover_block hbpart">
  <div class="atos_hover_block_image" style="height:500px;background-image: url(https://atos.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/boy-kite-flying-near-wind-turbies-banner-light.webp); background-position: 85% center;"></div>
  <div class="atos_hover_block_content shadow bg_white pad1220 hbleft" style="margin-top: -150px"><div><h3>Sustainability</h3>
<p>Explore sustainability services that drive measurable impact. Our experts embed ESG into IT and business operations, using AI and data platforms to meet compliance requirements and deliver meaningful, lasting change across your organization.</p>
<div style="margin-top: 10px;"><a class="button-blue" href="https://atos.net/en/services/sustainability-services">Learn more</a></div>
</div></div>
</div></div></div></div>                </article>
            </section>
        </main>
